  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe and Asia. The aim of this clinical trial is to compare two
      recombinant factor VIII drugs, turoctocog alfa (recombinant factor VIII (N8)) with Advate®,
      in haemophilia A subjects, investigating the action and safety of the drugs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
